The white dragon represents the rational mind.\nThe red dragon represents the intuitive mind.\nThe computer is the mind.\nThe computer manufacturing genious is the brain.\nThe computer system is the consciousness.\nThe fact that there is no password is the fact that the consciousness is always open.\nThe red dragon going inside the computer system represents the intuitive mind going inside the rational mind.\nThe red dragon getting stuck inside the computer system represents the intuitive mind getting stuck inside the rational mind.\nThe white dragon destroying all the computers represents the rational mind destroying all of the intuitive mind.\nThe white dragon destroying all the computers is the way that the rational mind clears the intuitive mind.

